      "actionDate": "2026-03-03",
      "actionDesc": "Passed Senate",
      "text": "<p><strong>Nicholas Dockery Medal of Honor Act</strong></p><p>This bill authorizes the President to award the Medal of Honor to Nicholas&nbsp;Dockery (formerly known as Kareem N. Dockery), for his acts of valor on October 2, 2012, as a member of the Army while serving in Afghanistan, for which he was previously awarded the Silver Star.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-04-09T20:55:23Z",
      "versionCode": "55"
